# Generated sources under src/ are deliberately committed, following the
# convention of the upstream tree-sitter grammar repos: a consumer builds the
# Rust binding with `cc` alone and must not need the tree-sitter CLI. That
# covers parser.c, node-types.json, grammar.json, and the tree_sitter/*.h
# headers parser.c includes. Regenerate with `tree-sitter generate`.
